data.description: Welcome to 1745 El Cerrito Drive, Red Bluff, CA! This charming home boasts an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere. Enjoy energy efficiency with a solar system, complemented by a new HVAC system (2023) and water heater (2023). The kitchen features modern amenities, including a stainless steel refrigerator and gas range. The well-designed layout includes a large master bedroom on one side, providing privacy, while the other two bedrooms are situated on the opposite side. Revel in the fresh look of new paint and carpet throughout. Tucked away at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac, this residence offers tranquility on a large pie-shaped lot, fully fenced in. Dual RV access adds convenience to this wonderful home.
